headline: Better Dividend Stock: Williams vs. Kinder Morgan
summary: Kinder Morgan (NYSE: KMI) and Williams (NYSE: WMB) are two of the largest natural gas pipeline companies in the country.  Many investors will take one look at the dividend yields currently offered by Kinder Morgan and Williams and automatically assume that Kinder Morgan's higher-yielding payout makes it the better option.
